# Product Price Prediction from Text

This project explores **predicting product prices** based on product descriptions using machine learning and natural language processing (NLP) techniques.  

Even without structured numerical features, the model achieves reasonable accuracy by extracting meaningful patterns from text.

---

## Dataset

- `train.csv` — contains product descriptions (`catalog_content`) and target prices (`price`), with 75,000 rows.  
- `test.csv` — contains product descriptions without prices (not used in this project, since real prices are unknown).  

